- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of optimization techniques and the application to robotics may also suggest a connection to artificial intelligence.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): While the paper does not focus on software engineering, the use of sum-of-squares programming and the S-procedure for computation may suggest a connection to software engineering.
